qRKcZ2hWjothgXI8CA4Q">Trịnh Sâm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/Qu%C3%A1-Hoa-Thanh-cung-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-SgKbXmywCkKgKkSGZDvCKg">Quá Hoa Thanh cung kỳ 2 - 過華清宮其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/author-3vzgm_fq7JLuFBSuENsFJw">Đỗ Mục</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/Qu%C3%BD-H%E1%BB%A3i-l%E1%BA%A1p-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-ng%C5%A9-d%E1%BA%A1-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-Thi%E1%BA%BFu-Nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%91%C3%A1p-ho%E1%BA%A1-ch%C6%B0-giai-t%C3%A1c-h%E1%BB%B7-ph%E1%BB%A5c/poem-UyhRR53jTD1dNcb5KwP2-Q">Quý Hợi lạp nhị thập ngũ dạ đắc Thiếu Nguyên đáp hoạ chư giai tác hỷ phục - 癸亥腊二十五夜得少原答和諸佳作喜復</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/T%C3%B4-T%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%91%C3%ACnh-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-7M4Fe8cLDWEI5eYDjDjRDw">Tô Tần đình kỳ 1 - 蘇秦亭其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Hoa/Tr%C3%A1ng-s%C4%A9-thi%C3%AAn/poem-sl-GLi45DPgtnGqUSPc7eA">Tráng sĩ thiên - 壯士篇</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Hoa/author-o1iv95c6q7O3ITieb1tGAg">Trương Hoa</a>)<br></div>	</div>
